videos.headline: Miami opens scoring with 2-yd TD pass
videos.description: Malik Rosier floats one up to TE Will Mallory, who brings it down and gives the Hurricanes a 7-0 lead.

videos.headline: Rosier crosses plane on QB sneak
videos.description: Miami QB Malik Rosier gets behind his blockers for a 1-yard touchdown carry.

videos.headline: Rosier fires strike for 67-yd TD
videos.description: Hurricanes QB Malik Rosier goes between the numbers and hits WR Jeff Thomas, who fights his way down the sideline to make it 21-0.

videos.headline: Miami converts in red-zone with 8-yd TD pass
videos.description: Hurricanes QB N'Kosi Perry delivers a bullet to WR Lawrence Cager, who crosses the goal-line and extends the lead to 28-0.

videos.headline: Hurricanes open 2nd half with TD
videos.description: QB N'Kosi Perry hits a wide-open Brevin Jordan for a 3-yard touchdown, making it 35-0 Miami.

videos.headline: Miami debuts new turnover chain after fumble recovery
videos.description: Trajan Brandy dives on a Savannah State fumble, and gets to sport the Hurricanes' flashy, 7-lb. turnover chain.

videos.headline: Miami DB climbs ladder for INT
videos.description: Sheldrick Redwine brings down an athletic interception and proceeds to show off the new turnover chain.

videos.headline: Miami RB breaks off 34-yd run to set up TD pass
videos.description: DeeJay Dallas bounces off tackles to get inside the 5-yard line, then WR Brevin Jordan finishes off the drive with a diving touchdown catch.

videos.headline: Miami backup QB keeps it for 16-yd TD
videos.description: Hurricanes QB Cade Weldon makes a man miss and charges into the end zone to continue the rout.

videos.headline: Dean makes INT to wear turnover chain
videos.description: Hurricanes DB Jhavonte Dean picks off TJ Bell and enjoys his turn with the turnover chain.

videos.headline: Miami blocks punt and recovers for TD
videos.description: Hurricanes DT Nesta Silvera bulldozes his way to the punter for a block, and then Scott Patchan scoops it up for a touchdown.

videos.headline: Miami defense gives turnover chain busy night
videos.description: Hurricanes LB Waynmon Steed falls on a fumble and gets him a moment with the turnover chain.

videos.headline: Hurricanes continue domination with TD run
videos.description: Miami QB Jarren Williams keeps it himself on the option play, fooling the defense to make it 70-0.

videos.headline: Miami RB makes electrifying 64-yd TD run
videos.description: Lorenzo Lingard makes the defense look silly and goes 64 yards for the final Hurricane touchdown of the game.
